313
00:33:29,759 --> 00:33:29,839
[UNKNOWN] Da.

314
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] U redu, sljedeća je Jam od Anya Obermuller, voditeljica digitalnog marketinga u RBI-u.

315
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:43,359
